commands.name: az monitor app-insights my-workbook list
commands.summary: List all private workbooks defined within a specified subscription and category.
commands.syntax:
az monitor app-insights my-workbook list --category {TSG, performance, retention, workbook}
                                         [--can-fetch-content {0, 1, f, false, n, no, t, true, y, yes}]
                                         [--max-items]
                                         [--next-token]
                                         [--resource-group]
                                         [--source-id]
                                         [--tags]
examples: az monitor app-insights my-workbook list  -g rg --category retention
